ActBank Act
SubjectDisclosure on Continuance Regulations (Federal Credit Unions)
PrecisDISCLOSURE ON CONTINUANCE REGULATIONS (FEDERAL CREDIT UNIONS) in order to specify the information that must be publicly disclosed to members and customers of the credit union and the process that must be followed to qualify the credit union to continue federally and be eligible for federal deposit insurance.
